=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMit.edu&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOexwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=eea50b14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mit.edu</a>唔得，但香港入到<br />\n<br />\n似乎麻省理工學院得罪左強國或強國領導，所以被block，厲害了我的國，連麻省理工都唔放左眼內。"},{"pid":"786e03cb254200965268fbc1d22299213a0df525","tid":1489464,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:57:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://viewdns.info/chinesefirewall/?domain=mit.edu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviewdns.info%2Fchinesefirewall%2F%3Fdomain%3Dmit.edu&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOexwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=64242fbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://viewdns.info/chinesefirewall/?domain=mit.edu</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UE0mVmB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUE0mVmB.png&h=d6de83d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度可以詳細些<br />\n原來想玩dns poisoning<br />\n而唔係完全封殺<br />\n即係類似你去麻省理工網站<br />\n但背後去左中國的網站<br />\n該網站可能都係拿返麻省理工網的野<br />\n但會被刪改一些內容"}]}